Marc Porel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marc_Porel 0 Marc Porel (3 January 1949 – 15 August 1983) was a Swiss-born French film actor. He appeared in 40 films between 1967 and 1983. He was born in Lausanne, Switzerland and died in Casablanca, Morocco of Meningitis. Marc_Porel ( 3_January_1949 – 15_August_1983 ) was a_Swiss-born_French_film_actor .
